data.description: Don't miss this beautiful home on a corner lot with tons of storage and room to play! Situated in a peaceful and family-friendly neighborhood, this property provides easy access to all the amenities Eugene has to offer. You'll find schools, parks, shopping centers, and dining options just a short drive away. The master suite has a spacious layout and en-suite bathroom. Additional bedrooms are perfect for a growing family, guests, or even a home office. Outside has a large front and backyard, deck, patio, Hot-tub, R.V. parking and more!
